E_CANNOT_INIT_CLIENT_ON_SERVER.message: The Radonis client cannot be initialized server-side. Make sure to only call `initClient` in the client bundle, typically in your `entry.client.ts` file

E_CANNOT_INIT_CLIENT_MULTIPLE_TIMES.message: The Radonis client cannot be initialized multiple times. Make sure to only initialize the client once in your application, typically in your `entry.client.ts` file
